# {{.Name}}

A workflow-based API service built with the [GoCodeAlone/workflow](https://github.com/GoCodeAlone/workflow) engine.

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Go 1.22+

### Run

```bash
go run . -config workflow.yaml
```

The server starts on port 8080.

### Endpoints

| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | /health | Health check |
| GET | /api/items | List items |
| POST | /api/items | Create item |
| GET | /api/items/{id} | Get item |
| PUT | /api/items/{id} | Update item |
| DELETE | /api/items/{id} | Delete item |

### Configuration

Edit `workflow.yaml` to add modules, routes, and workflows. See the
[workflow documentation](https://github.com/GoCodeAlone/workflow) for available module types.

### Build

```bash
go build -o {{.Name}} .
./{{.Name}} -config workflow.yaml
```

